# Слои бэкенда

Scope: `app/`, `database/`, `config/` (auth, domain). Только бэкенд.

## Структура

```
app/
├── Domain/{BC}/              # Ядро: Entities, Enums, ValueObjects, Repositories (ports), Services
├── Application/{BC}/         # Use cases: Commands, Handlers (orchestration)
├── Infrastructure/           # Adapters: Eloquent, Mappers, Repository implementations
│   └── Persistence/
│       ├── Eloquent/Models/
│       ├── Mappers/
│       └── Repositories/
└── Http/ | Filament/         # Driving adapters (presentation)
```

## Зависимости (Hexagonal)

- Domain — **zero** Laravel/Eloquent
- Application → Domain (ports)
- Infrastructure → Domain (implements ports)
- Presentation → Application

## Cross-BC

- Domain: только `*_id`, без foreign Eloquent relations
- Cross-BC orchestration — Application layer
- Read/query joins — Infrastructure или dedicated read models

## DI

Регистрация портов: `Infrastructure/Providers/PersistenceServiceProvider.php`
